Taking care of your new tumbler:

*Hand wash only.

*Not dishwasher safe

*Not microwave safe

*Do not leave in hot car for long periods of time

*Do not soak.

Note:

*Tumblers are handmade. I do my best to ensure they are close to perfect as can be. Please be advised that imperfections are a possibility

*Colors may differ due to computer screen / monitor settings

*By placing an order, you agree to my current turnaround time of 3-4 business days

*Not responsible for buyer error

*If there is an issue with your order, please contact me to see if we can get it resolved.

*All custom orders are final

*Refunds will not be issued

*Any damage due to shipping needs to be addressed within 48 hours of delivery. No exceptions.

Thank you for supporting my small business!
